name: The Atomic Fern
directions: Two at the back of the bar. Both gender neutral.
comment: The owner and bartenders are chill. One of the bartenders said my legal name out loud once to confirm that it was my tab. I corrected with good humor, "yeah that's it but you don't have to say it too loud." They were very sincerely apologetic and said it wouldn't happen again. The owner is anti-fascist and we hang on occasion.

comment: Not sure if they have a policy but I assume they prefer if it's customers using it like most cafes/bars/restaurants. I don't think they'd necessarily stop you or say anything to you as two businesses operate on the premises.
